00:30:14.791 --> 00:30:16.000
and how it links up to...

605
00:30:41.291 --> 00:30:43.083
What is this?

606
00:30:43.166 --> 00:30:44.541
Oh. that's far too pink. Ken.

607
00:30:44.625 --> 00:30:45.541
We are subtle.

608
00:30:45.625 --> 00:30:47.208
