657
00:32:29.333 --> 00:32:31.166
- No. it's just a question.
- It's not really relevant.

658
00:32:31.250 --> 00:32:34.041
Well. I mean. you worshipped
that place. and Miranda.

659
00:32:34.125 --> 00:32:35.666
So. why'd you leave?

660
00:32:35.750 --> 00:32:37.333
