710
00:34:45.416 --> 00:34:47.791
Yeah. um. I-I didn't wanna...

711
00:34:47.875 --> 00:34:50.666
But we do have some
important work coming up.

712
00:34:50.750 --> 00:34:53.000
- Hmm. Oh. good.
- Uh... Um. I...

713
00:34:54.833 --> 00:34:56.333
I'm doing a Sasha Barnes profile.

