00:35:00.416 --> 00:35:04.583
You really have an interview set?

715
00:35:05.500 --> 00:35:07.125
Uh. close.

716
00:35:07.208 --> 00:35:09.541
I'm just locking in the details.
but I-I-I have an in.

717
00:35:09.625 --> 00:35:10.833
Hmm.

